# 🍎 Nutrition — Bold Fitness Tracker

Completely different visual world from the rest of SAVY. Sunny, high-energy, data-dense.

## 🎯 Vibe in One Line

> Bright yellow gym floor, ocean-blue chrome, magenta glass overlays. Fitness tracker energy.

## 🎨 Palette

| Token | Hex | Role |
|-------|-----|------|
| SUN | `#F4D160` | Full-page background — the ground color |
| OCEAN | `#1D5D9B` | Primary buttons, FAB, active tab, interactive chrome |
| CHARCOAL | `#2C2C2C` | Text on yellow — NOT black, warm dark |
| GLASS | `rgba(176,30,104,0.9)` | Frosted panels — tabs, macro rings, food rows |
| GLASS_BORDER | `rgba(255,255,255,0.15)` | Subtle white border on glass panels |
| ORANGE | `#F49D1A` | Rotation food label, dinner meal button |
| GREEN | `#27AE60` | Success states |

### Meal Button Colors

| Meal | Color |
|------|-------|
| Breakfast | `#B01E68` |
| Lunch | `#1D5D9B` |
| Dinner | `#F49D1A` |
| Snack | `#DC3535` |

## 📐 Layout

- Max width: **480px** centered — mobile-first, single column
- Glass panels: `backdropFilter: blur(16px)`, `border-radius: 12-16px`
- FAB: **64px circle**, ocean blue, centered bottom, heavy blue shadow `0 6px 20px rgba(29,93,155,0.4)`
- Modals: dark scrim `rgba(0,0,0,0.5-0.6)`, glass sheet from bottom

## 🔤 Typography

| Element | Font | Size | Weight |
|---------|------|------|--------|
| Page title | Playfair Display | 28px | **700** (heavier than other pages!) |
| Subtitle | Inter | 11px | 600, uppercase, tracked |
| Tab labels | Inter | 12px | 700, tracked |
| Section title | Playfair Display | 18px | 700 |
| Food name | Inter | 13px | 600 |
| Macro data | Inter | 11px | 400 |
| Calorie value | Inter | 13px | 700, color: SUN `#F4D160` |

## 🧊 Glass Panel Pattern

```
┌─────────────────────────┐
│  background: GLASS       │  rgba(176,30,104,0.9)
│  border: GLASS_BORDER    │  rgba(255,255,255,0.15)
│  border-radius: 12-16px  │
│  backdrop-filter: blur   │  16-24px
│  text: white / 0.4-0.5   │
└─────────────────────────┘
```

## ✅ Do

- Use SUN yellow as page ground — always
- Glass panels for data containers, search, modals
- Ocean blue for primary actions (FAB, buttons, active tabs)
- Calorie numbers in SUN yellow on dark glass
- `backdrop-filter: blur()` on all glass panels

## 🚫 Don't

- Don't use cream `#F5F0E8` — that's the home/editorial palette
- Don't use crimson `#DC143C` for CTAs — use ocean `#1D5D9B`
- Don't use Playfair italic here — Playfair 700 bold, no italic
- Don't use standard card shadows — glass blur + borders create depth
- Don't bring editorial/journal typography into nutrition
